{"model_key": "cosyvoice3", "model_name": "CosyVoice3-0.5B", "model_size_params": "500M", "is_llm_based": true, "supported_languages": ["ko", "en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "ja", "method": "A", "ref_key": "ja_female", "text_key": "ja_medium", "text": "人工知能音声合成技術は目覚ましい進歩を遂げています。自然言語処理と深層学習の組み合わせにより、より自然で流暢な音声合成が実現されています。", "wav_path": "results_multilingual\\wav\\ja\\A\\cosyvoice3__ja_medium_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 22.18983840000874, "ttfa_ms": 5486.52609999408, "inference_time_s": 5.490114599990193, "audio_duration_s": 9.64, "rtf": 0.5695, "sample_rate": 24000, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 3284.8349609375, "vram_peak_mb": 3573.078125, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T08:36:35.126129"}
{"model_key": "cosyvoice3", "model_name": "CosyVoice3-0.5B", "model_size_params": "500M", "is_llm_based": true, "supported_languages": ["ko", "en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "ja", "method": "A", "ref_key": "ja_female", "text_key": "ja_formal", "text": "皆様、本日はお集まりいただきありがとうございます。弊社はこの十年間、継続的な成長を遂げてまいりました。今後ともご支援ご協力のほど、よろしくお願い申し上げます。", "wav_path": "results_multilingual\\wav\\ja\\A\\cosyvoice3__ja_formal_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 22.057692899994436, "ttfa_ms": 3839.8849999939557, "inference_time_s": 3.8432095000025583, "audio_duration_s": 6.32, "rtf": 0.6081, "sample_rate": 24000, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 3284.8349609375, "vram_peak_mb": 3572.0205078125, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T08:37:14.038982"}
