{"model_key": "gpt_sovits", "model_name": "GPT-SoVITS-V3", "model_size_params": "~200M", "is_llm_based": true, "supported_languages": ["ko", "en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "en", "method": "A", "ref_key": "en_female", "text_key": "en_names", "text": "Apple CEO Tim Cook met with Microsoft founder Bill Gates in New York City last Tuesday. Their discussion focused on arti", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\en\\A\\gpt_sovits__en_names_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 3.8876160999934655, "ttfa_ms": 6751.678400003584, "inference_time_s": 6.751678400003584, "audio_duration_s": 20.554666666666666, "rtf": 0.3285, "sample_rate": 24000, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1924.83056640625, "vram_peak_mb": 2259.36572265625, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:32:23.042543"}
{"model_key": "gpt_sovits", "model_name": "GPT-SoVITS-V3", "model_size_params": "~200M", "is_llm_based": true, "supported_languages": ["ko", "en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "en", "method": "A", "ref_key": "en_female", "text_key": "en_emotional", "text": "I'm so incredibly excited to share this news with you! After years of hard work, countless setbacks, and unwavering dedi", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\en\\A\\gpt_sovits__en_emotional_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 3.8650305999908596, "ttfa_ms": 7122.43919998582, "inference_time_s": 7.12243919998582, "audio_duration_s": 23.2, "rtf": 0.307, "sample_rate": 24000, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1924.83056640625, "vram_peak_mb": 2296.96875, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:33:09.733535"}
{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "ja", "method": "A", "ref_key": "ja_female", "text_key": "ja_short", "text": "こんにちは。今日はとても良い天気ですね。", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\ja\\A\\fish_speech__ja_short_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 7.151824400003534, "ttfa_ms": 3321.254800001043, "inference_time_s": 3.3213251999986824, "audio_duration_s": 2.7399546485260773, "rtf": 1.2122, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1708.41455078125, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:33:43.793553"}
{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "ja", "method": "A", "ref_key": "ja_female", "text_key": "ja_medium", "text": "人工知能音声合成技術は目覚ましい進歩を遂げています。自然言語処理と深層学習の組み合わせにより、より自然で流暢な音声合成が実現されています。", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\ja\\A\\fish_speech__ja_medium_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 7.102117799993721, "ttfa_ms": 14894.81660000456, "inference_time_s": 14.895549799999571, "audio_duration_s": 13.003174603174603, "rtf": 1.1455, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1708.71142578125, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:34:41.166505"}
{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "ja", "method": "A", "ref_key": "ja_female", "text_key": "ja_formal", "text": "皆様、本日はお集まりいただきありがとうございます。弊社はこの十年間、継続的な成長を遂げてまいりました。今後ともご支援ご協力のほど、よろしくお願い申し上げます。", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\ja\\A\\fish_speech__ja_formal_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 6.93868599999405, "ttfa_ms": 11640.93700000376, "inference_time_s": 11.641489000001457, "audio_duration_s": 10.031020408163265, "rtf": 1.1605, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1713.50927734375, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:35:30.598400"}
{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "ja", "method": "A", "ref_key": "ja_female", "text_key": "ja_conversational", "text": "ねえ、今日の昼ご飯どうする？ラーメンかカレーか迷ってるんだけど。最近寒いし、温かいものが食べたいよね。あなたはどう思う？", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\ja\\A\\fish_speech__ja_conversational_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 6.9391506999963894, "ttfa_ms": 9922.773500002222, "inference_time_s": 9.923402500004158, "audio_duration_s": 8.823582766439909, "rtf": 1.1246, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1708.416015625, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:36:16.506747"}
