{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "zh", "method": "A", "ref_key": "zh_female", "text_key": "zh_short", "text": "你好，今天天气真不错。", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\zh\\A\\fish_speech__zh_short_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 6.897604099998716, "ttfa_ms": 2160.861099997419, "inference_time_s": 2.16092860000208, "audio_duration_s": 1.6718367346938776, "rtf": 1.2925, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1708.41455078125, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:41:09.141006"}
{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "zh", "method": "A", "ref_key": "zh_female", "text_key": "zh_medium", "text": "人工智能语音合成技术取得了令人瞩目的进展。自然语言处理和深度学习的结合使得语音合成更加自然流畅。", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\zh\\A\\fish_speech__zh_medium_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 6.91805460001342, "ttfa_ms": 10524.293099995703, "inference_time_s": 10.524864799997886, "audio_duration_s": 9.241541950113378, "rtf": 1.1389, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1708.41552734375, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:41:55.599288"}
{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "zh", "method": "A", "ref_key": "zh_female", "text_key": "zh_formal", "text": "尊敬的各位来宾，感谢您出席本次活动。我公司在过去十年中取得了长足的发展，在全球市场上建立了强大的竞争优势。未来，我们将继续努力，不负各方期望。", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\zh\\A\\fish_speech__zh_formal_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 6.989295599996694, "ttfa_ms": 15479.792999991332, "inference_time_s": 15.480540499993367, "audio_duration_s": 13.421133786848072, "rtf": 1.1534, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1742.57275390625, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:42:53.601824"}
{"model_key": "fish_speech", "model_name": "Fish-Speech-1.5", "model_size_params": "~500M", "is_llm_based": false, "supported_languages": ["en", "ja", "zh"], "lang": "zh", "method": "A", "ref_key": "zh_female", "text_key": "zh_conversational", "text": "哎，你今天中午吃什么？我想吃火锅，最近天气冷，吃点热乎的最舒服了。你有什么想法吗？", "wav_path": "D:\\tts-benchmark\\results\\results_multilingual\\wav\\zh\\A\\fish_speech__zh_conversational_0.wav", "success": true, "load_time_s": 7.2356263999972725, "ttfa_ms": 7728.150599999935, "inference_time_s": 7.728543100005481, "audio_duration_s": 6.780226757369615, "rtf": 1.1399, "sample_rate": 44100, "vram_before_mb": 0.0, "vram_after_mb": 1561.98974609375, "vram_peak_mb": 1708.41552734375, "cer": null, "wer": null, "stt_text": null, "timestamp": "2026-03-05T09:43:36.688956"}
